Data Notice (data/ directory)

The conversation data under data/ (chat logs, their JSON form, and the
gold-standard annotations) comes from the x-GDP experiment (Parady, Oyama &
Chikaraishi, 2025, Transportation 52, 413-437,
https://doi.org/10.1007/s11116-023-10426-9), collected under IRB-approved
protocols and anonymized for release.

The data is provided for RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, and is not covered by the
MIT License above. If you use the data, cite the x-GDP methodology paper and
the paper associated with this repository. Do not redistribute the data
separately from this repository, attempt to re-identify participants, or use
it for non-research purposes without contacting the authors first.
